# HCMO 0.2.0 compatibility mappings for published 0.0.1 IRIs.
# This module contains no new concepts. Invalid non-HCMO namespace artifacts are
# archived under ontology/legacy/mapp-0.0.1 and are not part of this graph.

@prefix dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
